import "./AboutContentStyles2.css"; import React from 'react' const AboutContent2 = () => { return (

EDUCATION

2018 - 2021

High School Degree

Kafaraakka Oficial School
Kafaraakka Al Koura, Lebanon
Graduated: june 2021
-Prom Leader

2021 - 2025

Bachelor's Degree

Bachelor of science in Computer Science
American University Of Culture and Education
Graduated: February 2025

EXPERIENCE

2023 - 2024

Full Stack Training

Proficient in full-stack development, with expertise in both front-end (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, ReactJS) and back-end (NodeJS, Express) technologies. Adept at designing and implementing scalable, efficient, and secure web applications. Gained experience with database management (MongoDB, MSQL).

2021 - 2024

Red Cross

Active volunteer with Youth Red Cross, engaging in humanitarian efforts and community service projects. Participate in outreach programs, disaster relief activities, and health education campaigns. Develop teamwork, empathy, and crisis management skills through dedicated service. Strengthen commitment to social responsibility and making a positive impact on community welfare.

2018 - 2024

Snack Johnny Manager

Successfully managed day-to-day operations, overseeing inventory, sales, and customer service. Implemented strategic marketing initiatives, resulting in an increase in customers and revenues. Trained and supervised a team of employees, achieving high levels of customer satisfaction.

2022 - 2024

Leader

Led a summer festival where all profits directly supported a charitable cause. Organized and managed event logistics, overseeing a team of volunteers and staff. Implemented strategic planning to maximize profitability and ensure smooth operations. Successfully contributed significant funds to our designated charitable cause, reflecting our commitment to community impact.

) } export default AboutContent2
